        "content": "<p>111. <span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">寫出</span>C++<span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">程式碼說明傳值呼叫</span>call by value<span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">。</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>#include &lt;iostream&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>using namespace std;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>int add2(int a, int b) {</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a = a + b;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; return a ;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>void add1(int &amp; a, int b) {</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a = a + b;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>void add(int a, int b) {</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a = a + b;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>int main() {</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; int a = 1;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; int b = 2;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; add( a, b) ;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; printf(&quot;%d\\n&quot;, a) ; // a=1 (a<span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">沒變</span>)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; add1( a, b) ;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; printf(&quot;%d\\n&quot;, a); // a = 1+2 = 3 (a<span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">變了</span>)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; printf(&quot;%d&quot;, add2( a, b)); a = 3+2 = 5 (a<span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">變了</span>)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; return 0;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>}</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 最終</span>a<span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">印出</span>1<span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">的原因是此為</span>call by value<span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">的程式碼，程式碼只是在</span>add function <span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">中把</span>a<span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">和</span>b<span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">的值拿去做運算，在</span>main function<span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">中並不會改變</span>a<span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">的值，若想把</span>a<span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">值改變，方法有</span>1.(add1 function)<span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">在</span>int a<span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">中間加入</span>&amp;<span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">符號</span> 2.(add2 function)<span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">把</span>void<span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">改為</span>int<span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">，</span>return a<span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">，並印出</span>add(a, b)<span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">。</span></p>",
